  "_comment": [
    "Benchmark sweep configuration for the art_simple ART reconstruction example.",
    "Each scenario maps to one BenchmarkScenario object in metrics_collector.py.",
    "",
    "app_args positional order (matches prompt.txt execution example):",
    "  <hdf5_input>  <center>  <num_iter>  <num_threads>  <start_angle_idx>  <num_angles>",
    "",
    "Design:",
    "  - Fixed 4 MPI processes for all scenarios.",
    "  - 3 workload sizes controlled by num_iter (outer iterations):",
    "      short  : num_iter = 3",
    "      medium : num_iter = 5",
    "      long   : num_iter = 10",
    "  - For each workload: 1 failure-free baseline + 5 failure scenarios",
    "    with injection delays of 10s, 20s, 40s, 80s, and 160s.",
    "  - Total: 3 × (1 + 5) = 18 scenarios.",
    "",
    "Set DATA_PATH env var to override the default HDF5 input path.",
    "Default: build/data/tooth_preprocessed.h5 (resolved via DATA_PATH env var in run_art_simple_validation.sh)"
  ],
